data.enText: a small spoon for putting sugar into tea and other drinks
the amount a teaspoon can hold

tr: a small spoon used for stirring tea or coffee
as much as a teaspoon will hold

value.def: A teaspoon is a small spoon that you use to put sugar into tea or coffee.

example.ex: Drop the dough onto a baking sheet with a teaspoon.
example.tran: 用茶匙把生面团舀到烤盘上。

value.def: You can refer to an amount of food resting on a teaspoon as a teaspoon of food.

example.ex: He wants three teaspoons of sugar in his coffee.
example.tran: 他要在咖啡里放 3 茶匙的糖。
